Package: bulldog
Architecture: amd64
Depends: coreutils (>= 7), bsd-mailx (>= 7), lsb-base (>= 7)
Description: Check if websites are reachable
 Bulldog is an amazing hunting dog that checks for you a list of URLs and warns
 you by email if one of them returns a http code that is not 200.
